Business Brief -- Bergen Brunswig Corp.:
   Company Is Discussing Sale
   Of 80%-Owned Commtron
Bergen Brunswig, Orange, Calif., is a distributor of
prescription drugs and health care products. Commtron is a
national distributor of prerecorded videocassettes.
   Robert E. Martini, president of Bergen Brunswig, said that
Bergen Brunswig and its shareholders "would be better served
if Bergen Brunswig concentrated exclusively on pharmaceutical
distribution, which has always been its principal business."